Package com.aloqa.trax.shared.saps.exceptions

Exception Summary
RejectedAPICallException An instance of this exception is thrown whenever it was not possible to process an invocation to TraXAPI_SAP_App.addObservation(com.aloqa.trax.shared.saps.AsynchronousRequest), TraXAPI_SAP_App.removeObservation(String, String), or TraXAPI_SAP_App.synchRequest(String, com.aloqa.trax.shared.saps.SynchronousRequest).
